  "detailed_description": "CTRL+ALT+REPEAT is a multiplayer 3D parkour platformer where you race against the clock and your friends. The game features 64 hand crafted levels across 4 worlds requiring patience and focus to complete.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlockable Movement Mechanics</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Double Jump<br></li><li> Sliding<br></li><li> Wall Running<br></li><li> Grappling<br></li><li> Rail Grinding<br></li><li> Gliding</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some Obstacles You'll Encounter</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Sweepers <br></li><li> Ferris Wheels<br></li><li> Lava<br></li><li> Jump Pads<br></li><li> Rotating Drums<br></li><li> Conveyor Belts<br></li><li> Boulders</li></ul><br>Are you up to the challenge?",
